  "title": "Cleaner (part time)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>· Responsible for all basic cleaning within the premise (cleaning &amp; mopping the floor, emptying the trash bins, cleaning the glass door, disinfection etc)</p>\n<p>· Wash basins, sinks and clean toilets</p>\n<p>· Any other duties assigned by the superior</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>· Some relevant work experience is preferred</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p>\n<p>· 4 worked days x 4 hours OR</p>\n<p>· 5 worked days x 4 hours</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Please WhatsApp your resume to 90700919. Alternatively, you may email us your resume to <a href=\"mailto:human.resources@gimanbeauty.com\">human.resources@gimanbeauty.com</a></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified for interview.</p>",
